Package: multiomicsretina
Title: Reproducible Multi-Omics Integration Pipeline for Human Retinal Research
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Project", "Maintainer", email = "maintainer@example.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Research-oriented hybrid pipeline for preprocessing, quality
    control, exploratory analysis, and downstream interpretation of
    externally trained MOFA2 models for proteomics, lipidomics, and
    metabolomics data from human retinal studies.
